Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
fp_vertical_row(25.10)                                  fp_vertical_row(25.10)

Name
       fp_vertical_row

Syntax
       fp_vertical_row {0 | 1}

       Type: Integer

       Default: 0

       Specifies whether the rows in the floorplan are vertical or horizontal.
       By default, the rows in the floorplan are horizontal. Set this variable
       to 1 to enable vertical rows.

Example
              * The following command sets the rows in the floorplan to verti-
                cal.

                set fp_vertical_row 1

Related Information
              * init_design

